  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "1982-04-15", 
    "text": "State Veterans' Home Amendments of 1982 - Postpones until 1984 the Administrator of Veterans' Affairs report to the Veterans' Affairs committees of Congress on the alcohol and drug dependence treatment pilot program. Authorizes appropriations through FY 1986 for grants to State nursing facilities for care of veterans. Permits the Administrator to make arrangements for Veterans Administration facilities to share medical resources and information with State home facilities."
